style=3D'color:#6B26FF;text-decoration:none'>Portland =
stabbing</span></a>, I wrote&nbsp;<a =
href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJw9kE1uxCAMhU8zLCP-IQsW3XTZKyAS=
